metadata.name: CO-EXISTENCE
metadata.description:
*𝘗𝘭𝘦𝘢𝘴𝘦 𝘵𝘶𝘳𝘯 𝘵𝘩𝘦 𝘴𝘰𝘶𝘯𝘥 𝘰𝘯*

"CO-EXISTENCE is a vision where technology and nature not only live in harmony, but where they also complement each other.

Helping each other grow. 

Amidst this, an entity finds herself meditating amongst this divine interconnection. 

It represents our ability to co-exist in this world in spite of the differences! How wonderful can the world be, if we could just learn to co-exist."

More Info: Original Soundtrack was created for this animation by the Creator. The first Primary Collector receives 3 High Quality 4K stills.
